Tarea completada
I've built the Well Assurance management app for Oil & Gas operations, featuring a dark industrial aesthetic with amber/orange accents. The app includes:

4 Screens:

Active Forecast (Home) - Child PADs list with case status summaries and search
Cases List - Cases per Child PAD with create/delete dialogs and business rule validation
Case Detail - Status management, editable fields, Parent Wells gallery, and auto-Case 2 creation
Parent Well Form - Role-based field permissions with status-aware editing
Business Rules Implemented:

Only one Draft/Open case per Child PAD
Case 3 requires all previous cases Closed/Cancelled
Parent Wells frozen when case is Open
CdG can only edit Orden Interna for AB/AD types
Reservoir can edit Presión Inicial when Carga Manual WHPI is enabled (Draft only)
Assurance has contingency edit rights with mandatory justification
Closing Case 3 auto-creates Case 2


